The speaker introduces the concept of Generative AI, emphasising its application in creating new, original content including text, images or even audio, through a user prompt. She highlights the extensive training data necessary for AI to produce unique and pertinent responses. She moves towards discussing its utility within Wonka Industries, suggesting its efficiency in tasks like writing emails or reports. Lastly, she draws attention towards Wonka Industries's likely initial use of AI to generate text, hinting towards the adoption of Large Language Models (LLMs) technology.